  "volume": 150000,\n    "open_interest": 50000,\n    "price_updated_at": "2026-
04-01T20:00:00Z"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### `GET /api/markets/:ticker/history`\n
\nGet price history (candles or raw snapshots).\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n\n| Pa
rameter | Type | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| `resolutio
n` | string | `1m`, `5m`, `15m`, `1h`, `1d` (default: `1d`) |\n| `days` | number
| Last N days (default: `7`, max: `365`) |\n| `from` | string | Start timestamp 
