n\n---\n\n### `GET /api/orders/:id`\n\nGet order by ID.\n\n**Response:**\n\n```j
son\n{\n  "order": {\n    "id": "...",\n    "ticker": "INXW-25-DEC31",\n    "sid
e": "yes",\n    "action": "buy",\n    "contracts": 100,\n    "price": 65,\n    "
